WEBVTT

00:00:00.067 --> 00:00:01.195
(Previously)
Since you're chasing these cats

00:00:01.219 --> 00:00:02.716
to make your mother's dream come true,

00:00:02.740 --> 00:00:04.689
don't you want to help fulfill
another dream of hers too?

00:00:04.713 --> 00:00:06.133
You didn't ruin her life.

00:00:06.672 --> 00:00:08.432
But you made her…
still alive in this world.

00:00:08.893 --> 00:00:10.653
I believe your mom is
always there with you.

00:00:10.852 --> 00:00:14.339
Mom said whoever
collects all 9 cats together

00:00:14.579 --> 00:00:16.499
will be friends until old age.

00:00:16.706 --> 00:00:19.406
Who are you calling a
friend? I'm your boyfriend.

00:00:19.760 --> 00:00:21.160
Why do you want to be my boyfriend?

00:00:21.793 --> 00:00:24.900
When you want a cat, do you need a reason?

00:00:29.288 --> 00:00:30.303
Here, Grandpa.

00:00:31.536 --> 00:00:32.896
Mom wrote in here

00:00:33.047 --> 00:00:35.694
that you let her go out to celebrate
her graduation with friends.

00:00:36.067 --> 00:00:37.415
She also wrote about

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:39.867
a mission to find nine cats.

00:00:41.191 --> 00:00:43.254
I completed that on her behalf.

00:00:46.982 --> 00:00:47.982
I'm sorry.

00:00:48.340 --> 00:00:49.592
This is all I could do for her.

00:00:50.202 --> 00:00:52.817
I wish she could've been the one
to complete it herself.

00:00:55.928 --> 00:00:57.121
No need to apologize.

00:00:59.436 --> 00:01:01.390
I should be thanking you.

00:01:02.888 --> 00:01:04.957
(After you were born…)

00:01:05.431 --> 00:01:07.810
(even though I never spoke
to your mom again, )

00:01:08.249 --> 00:01:11.488
(it didn't mean I stopped
worrying about her.)

00:01:12.294 --> 00:01:18.151
(Until the day I saw her smile,
a smile I'd never seen on her before, )

00:01:18.491 --> 00:01:21.908
(I knew right away
I didn't have to worry anymore.)

00:01:31.650 --> 00:01:32.650
Take it.

00:01:34.460 --> 00:01:35.900
Thank you so much…

00:01:38.251 --> 00:01:40.511
for making my daughter happy.

00:01:43.080 --> 00:01:44.087
You should keep it.

00:01:45.057 --> 00:01:47.500
Read it when you miss your mom.

00:01:53.114 --> 00:01:54.566
Thank you so much, Grandpa, Grandma.

00:01:57.299 --> 00:01:58.995
Alright, we'll head back now.

00:01:59.486 --> 00:02:01.897
Please take care of yourselves.

00:02:03.676 --> 00:02:04.676
Goodbye.

00:02:04.733 --> 00:02:06.023
Have a safe trip home.

00:02:06.714 --> 00:02:08.807
Alright, you should get going.

00:02:08.894 --> 00:02:11.136
Look, I've got something for you too.

00:02:13.802 --> 00:02:16.020
Alright then. Goodbye, sir.

00:02:17.435 --> 00:02:18.435
Wait.

00:02:20.648 --> 00:02:22.443
I may be old,

00:02:24.238 --> 00:02:25.716
but I remember

00:02:26.867 --> 00:02:28.547
every promise made to me.

00:02:32.994 --> 00:02:34.187
Don't you worry, sir.

00:02:35.230 --> 00:02:38.711
I'll make sure Lynx can hear the cats
and love them.

00:02:39.610 --> 00:02:40.610
Good.

00:02:41.018 --> 00:02:43.111
And I have one more request.

00:02:46.054 --> 00:02:47.975
Please take good care of Lynx for me.

00:02:48.533 --> 00:02:51.520
Even if you didn't ask,

00:02:53.098 --> 00:02:54.220
I'd still do it.

00:02:55.988 --> 00:02:56.988
Thanks.

00:03:03.552 --> 00:03:04.552
Thanks a lot.

00:03:15.958 --> 00:03:17.395
I've got something for you, Jumbo.

00:03:18.263 --> 00:03:20.207
Look, Jumbo.

00:03:21.513 --> 00:03:22.900
But don't tell your dads,

00:03:23.293 --> 00:03:24.820
or they'll say I'm spoiling you.

00:03:25.007 --> 00:03:26.007
Got it?

00:03:37.153 --> 00:03:38.153
Oh shit.

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:34.000
"Cat for Cash"
(Episode 7)

00:04:41.993 --> 00:04:43.106
You go in first.

00:04:43.360 --> 00:04:44.400
I'll bring the stuff in.

00:04:44.529 --> 00:04:45.529
Okay.

00:05:14.727 --> 00:05:15.246
Hey!

00:05:15.271 --> 00:05:16.353
What are you doing?

00:05:16.480 --> 00:05:17.500
Good, you're here.

00:05:19.759 --> 00:05:20.766
Where's that bastard?

00:05:21.106 --> 00:05:21.726
Who?

00:05:21.840 --> 00:05:22.853
I asked where he is!

00:05:22.893 --> 00:05:24.103
Who are you even talking about?!

00:05:24.127 --> 00:05:25.127
Ouch!

00:05:28.033 --> 00:05:29.033
Are you alright?

00:05:29.100 --> 00:05:30.346
I don't know who they're after.

00:05:57.472 --> 00:05:58.672
Who the hell are you bastards?

00:06:03.520 --> 00:06:04.713
Fine, don't answer.

00:06:06.520 --> 00:06:07.880
Go tell your boss

00:06:09.253 --> 00:06:10.813
this place belongs to Hia Singha's son.

00:06:11.653 --> 00:06:13.093
Unless you want trouble with my dad,

00:06:14.013 --> 00:06:15.653
don't you dare show
your faces here again.

00:06:16.500 --> 00:06:17.500
No!

00:06:20.027 --> 00:06:21.147
Hey, let's go.

00:06:30.453 --> 00:06:31.493
Are you okay?

00:06:32.286 --> 00:06:33.606
I'm okay. You?

00:06:35.347 --> 00:06:36.347
I'm fine.

00:06:36.767 --> 00:06:38.020
Let's go check on our kids.

00:06:41.779 --> 00:06:42.899
Are they okay?

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:51.160
Jumbo.

00:06:59.113 --> 00:07:00.233
What a relief.

00:07:01.327 --> 00:07:02.580
Good thing I've got quick eyes.

00:07:07.193 --> 00:07:09.293
So those guys
were looking for you, Leo?

00:07:13.566 --> 00:07:14.566
Sort of.

00:07:18.960 --> 00:07:19.960
Well…

00:07:21.480 --> 00:07:24.593
I used to serve at a bar.

00:07:25.853 --> 00:07:28.406
One day, a customer
lavished money on me.

00:07:29.486 --> 00:07:32.326
How was I supposed to know that
customer was some big shot's kept lover?

00:07:32.704 --> 00:07:33.791
That's why I fled here.

00:07:34.160 --> 00:07:35.160
What?

00:07:35.431 --> 00:07:37.751
Who would've thought
they would follow me all the way here?

00:07:38.649 --> 00:07:39.809
Sorry about all this, though.

00:07:42.143 --> 00:07:43.143
Sorry?

00:07:44.308 --> 00:07:45.413
Go say sorry to the cats.

00:07:46.018 --> 00:07:47.201
They are Mom's cats.

00:07:47.472 --> 00:07:48.961
Did it even cross your mind
to protect them?

00:07:48.985 --> 00:07:50.160
What did you expect me to do?

00:07:50.389 --> 00:07:52.461
Just stand there and let them
beat the crap out of me?

00:07:52.485 --> 00:07:53.485
Enough!

00:07:54.603 --> 00:07:56.107
The cats are already freaking out.

00:07:57.445 --> 00:07:59.095
I shouldn't have let you stay.

00:08:02.338 --> 00:08:03.338
Who are you to say that?

00:08:05.428 --> 00:08:06.816
You think you're so damn righteous

00:08:07.934 --> 00:08:09.313
for taking in Dad's other kid?

00:08:11.018 --> 00:08:12.018
Let me break it to you.

00:08:12.535 --> 00:08:13.575
You're the mistress's kid.

00:08:14.585 --> 00:08:15.200
You get that?

00:08:15.441 --> 00:08:16.669
You were born from a mistress!

00:08:21.134 --> 00:08:22.222
Are you Meow?

00:08:22.860 --> 00:08:23.860
Yes.

00:08:26.310 --> 00:08:27.410
I'm Kao.

00:08:30.063 --> 00:08:31.349
I'm Wichien's wife.

00:08:34.554 --> 00:08:35.994
Even though you were born before me,

00:08:36.303 --> 00:08:38.036
Dad was with my mom first.

00:08:38.857 --> 00:08:40.387
You're the one who broke up my family.

00:08:47.274 --> 00:08:48.608
What happened today…

00:08:49.550 --> 00:08:52.605
is nothing compared to what I've
been through my whole life.

00:08:54.830 --> 00:08:58.020
If you weren't the only family I had left,

00:08:59.132 --> 00:09:00.732
I never would've set foot in this place.

00:09:32.094 --> 00:09:33.094
Lynx.

00:09:40.341 --> 00:09:41.341
I don't think…

00:09:43.320 --> 00:09:45.000
Leo meant it like that.

00:09:46.904 --> 00:09:48.624
Well, I was born from
Dad's mistress, right?

00:09:52.221 --> 00:09:53.493
What right do I have to be mad?

00:09:54.309 --> 00:09:55.412
Even so,

00:09:58.144 --> 00:09:59.398
you're still his older brother.

00:10:01.506 --> 00:10:03.811
Yes, I'm the older one.

00:10:09.360 --> 00:10:11.597
I'll fulfill my duties as a brother
as best as I can.

00:10:16.870 --> 00:10:17.870
Leo.

00:10:21.990 --> 00:10:23.114
Leo, open the door.

00:10:29.088 --> 00:10:30.411
Don't you want to know about Dad?

00:10:41.107 --> 00:10:42.107
Our dad's not dead.

00:10:45.243 --> 00:10:46.529
What crap are you talking about?

00:10:49.570 --> 00:10:51.293
WICHIEN

00:10:51.360 --> 00:10:53.510
There's something important
you should know.

00:10:54.234 --> 00:10:55.234
Yes, Grandma?

00:10:59.055 --> 00:11:01.309
This is your dad's phone number.

00:11:01.888 --> 00:11:04.852
You mom didn't want you to look for him,

00:11:05.207 --> 00:11:07.789
so she told you he was dead.

00:11:09.544 --> 00:11:12.103
When she found out
about her heart condition,

00:11:12.611 --> 00:11:14.508
she asked me to tell you.

00:11:15.401 --> 00:11:17.084
Honestly, I didn't want you to know.

00:11:17.392 --> 00:11:21.205
But your mom wanted you to know
you still have a father.

00:11:24.339 --> 00:11:27.492
What you do with this…
that's up to you.

00:11:27.997 --> 00:11:29.509
Now, you don't have just me left.

00:11:31.532 --> 00:11:32.612
What do you want to do now?

00:11:33.338 --> 00:11:34.618
Do you want to go live with him?

00:11:47.390 --> 00:11:52.395
(Please check the number and try again.
(Sorry. The number you—)

00:11:52.663 --> 00:11:53.943
Are you sure this is the number?

00:11:54.877 --> 00:11:56.093
He probably changed it.

00:11:57.725 --> 00:11:58.895
You don't have another one?

00:12:03.887 --> 00:12:04.989
I'll try to track it down.

00:12:06.644 --> 00:12:07.644
How?

00:12:08.838 --> 00:12:10.038
The number's no longer in use.

00:12:10.482 --> 00:12:11.592
I've got my ways.

00:12:18.116 --> 00:12:20.496
Hello. Dong...

00:12:30.311 --> 00:12:31.508
I got his address.

00:12:57.205 --> 00:12:58.205
You wait here.

00:13:00.681 --> 00:13:01.813
Let me go with you.

00:13:02.619 --> 00:13:04.299
He hurt you and Leo once.

00:13:04.500 --> 00:13:05.500
I know.

00:13:05.777 --> 00:13:06.892
But Leo's my brother.

00:13:07.291 --> 00:13:08.291
Let me handle this.

00:13:08.561 --> 00:13:09.561
But…

00:13:11.854 --> 00:13:14.907
Just seeing me and Leo
will shock him enough.

00:13:17.198 --> 00:13:20.560
If I bring my boyfriend along too,
it'll be a lot to deal with.

00:13:25.359 --> 00:13:26.390
Okay, fair enough.

00:13:27.400 --> 00:13:30.018
I'll wait here then.

00:13:43.237 --> 00:13:44.037
Thank you.

00:13:44.248 --> 00:13:45.248
Thank you.

00:13:46.914 --> 00:13:47.893
Please wait here for a moment.

00:13:47.918 --> 00:13:49.597
I'll let Mr. Wichien know you're here.

00:13:50.023 --> 00:13:51.023
Thank you.

00:14:08.298 --> 00:14:09.298
Are you Lynx?

00:14:21.175 --> 00:14:23.091
This is Leo, my brother.

00:14:29.586 --> 00:14:30.586
Leo…

00:14:32.722 --> 00:14:33.722
Kao's son?

00:14:35.391 --> 00:14:36.391
Yes…

00:14:37.722 --> 00:14:38.722
Dad.

00:14:47.133 --> 00:14:49.701
How did you two find me?

00:14:50.625 --> 00:14:51.705
It's a long story, Dad.

00:14:52.561 --> 00:14:56.016
Just know that both our moms…

00:14:58.207 --> 00:14:59.207
have passed away.

00:15:07.356 --> 00:15:08.608
I'm sorry for both of you.

00:15:20.310 --> 00:15:21.812
I've got no one left now.

00:15:23.082 --> 00:15:24.600
Can I stay here with you?

00:15:33.312 --> 00:15:36.313
I'm really glad to see both of my sons.

00:15:43.197 --> 00:15:44.717
But it's not really convenient for me.

00:15:49.520 --> 00:15:50.520
Why?

00:15:50.824 --> 00:15:52.775
You don't believe I'm your son?

00:15:52.947 --> 00:15:53.947
No, son. No.

00:15:54.602 --> 00:15:55.602
That's not it.

00:15:56.811 --> 00:15:57.933
Who are you talking to, Dad?

00:16:00.855 --> 00:16:01.855
Nothing.

00:16:03.749 --> 00:16:04.749
Nothing, sweetie.

00:16:14.407 --> 00:16:15.407
Your family?

00:16:20.643 --> 00:16:22.814
So what? I'm your son too.

00:16:23.582 --> 00:16:25.791
My mom was with you before anyone.

00:16:26.973 --> 00:16:27.973
Yes, son.

00:16:33.068 --> 00:16:34.988
But the people here
don't know about any of this.

00:16:35.398 --> 00:16:37.001
And they must never find out.

00:16:43.683 --> 00:16:44.683
That's right.

00:16:45.603 --> 00:16:47.100
I was with Kao before you.

00:16:51.932 --> 00:16:55.713
In that case, you should
go back to be with her.

00:16:56.453 --> 00:16:57.453
I'm okay with that.

00:17:00.274 --> 00:17:01.502
Though Kao came first,

00:17:03.710 --> 00:17:04.995
I cannot be with either of you.

00:17:07.051 --> 00:17:08.636
What do you mean?

00:17:09.155 --> 00:17:10.914
My family already
arranged my engagement.

00:17:12.295 --> 00:17:14.962
In two years, once that woman graduates,
I have to marry her.

00:17:17.562 --> 00:17:18.562
Whoa.

00:17:21.931 --> 00:17:26.309
So both Lynx and I…
are your secret families?

00:17:29.881 --> 00:17:30.881
I'm sorry.

00:17:32.601 --> 00:17:33.708
I didn't have a choice.

00:17:37.065 --> 00:17:38.692
The truth is, I never loved that woman.

00:17:39.989 --> 00:17:41.918
The only women I ever loved
were your moms.

00:17:46.840 --> 00:17:48.107
And you dare call that love?

00:17:51.845 --> 00:17:52.845
Are you done, Dad?

00:17:52.942 --> 00:17:54.305
I'm going to be late for my class.

00:17:54.654 --> 00:17:56.203
Done, sweetie. I'm done.

00:18:02.072 --> 00:18:03.304
Go home first.

00:18:04.284 --> 00:18:05.284
If anything,

00:18:06.226 --> 00:18:07.586
I'll contact you.

00:18:28.360 --> 00:18:29.360
How'd it go?

00:18:29.897 --> 00:18:30.897
Did you see him?

00:18:33.559 --> 00:18:34.937
Good thing you didn't go in there.

00:18:37.960 --> 00:18:38.960
Let's go.

00:18:51.282 --> 00:18:52.282
Leo.

00:18:52.662 --> 00:18:53.662
Leo!

00:18:53.734 --> 00:18:54.734
Lynx.

00:18:57.611 --> 00:18:58.635
Give him time.

00:19:00.007 --> 00:19:01.200
Give yourself time too.

00:19:03.274 --> 00:19:05.007
You both just went through
the same thing.

00:19:09.303 --> 00:19:10.460
That's nothing to me.

00:19:14.247 --> 00:19:15.247
How's everything?

00:19:15.387 --> 00:19:16.501
I heard what happened here.

00:19:17.286 --> 00:19:18.307
It's okay now, Dr. Pom.

00:19:18.851 --> 00:19:19.869
Everyone's safe.

00:19:20.739 --> 00:19:21.739
That's a relief.

00:19:22.058 --> 00:19:23.058
And the cats?

00:19:24.972 --> 00:19:26.869
Why haven't any of them eaten?

00:19:28.241 --> 00:19:29.497
Cats scare easily.

00:19:29.822 --> 00:19:32.098
When something frightening happens,
they hide

00:19:32.388 --> 00:19:33.554
because they don't feel safe.

00:19:35.752 --> 00:19:37.804
Everyone, it's safe now.

00:19:39.469 --> 00:19:40.506
Do you want to eat?

00:19:42.147 --> 00:19:43.147
Come eat.

00:19:43.766 --> 00:19:44.766
Lynx!

00:19:44.993 --> 00:19:45.993
I think…

00:19:46.404 --> 00:19:47.419
you should leave them be.

00:19:47.768 --> 00:19:49.309
They're still in shock.

00:19:50.301 --> 00:19:52.494
Let them calm down first,
then comfort them.

00:19:55.289 --> 00:19:56.709
How long will that take?

00:19:58.211 --> 00:19:59.705
It's hard to say.

00:20:00.261 --> 00:20:02.302
It depends on each cat
and what they went through.

00:20:02.876 --> 00:20:08.005
But as far as I know…
something like this takes time to heal.

00:20:09.988 --> 00:20:14.665
(Bro Jiro, will they come hit us again?)

00:20:46.237 --> 00:20:48.420
If you want to comfort someone,
go to the next room.

00:20:50.845 --> 00:20:51.845
I'm fine.

00:20:53.237 --> 00:20:54.254
Well, you said it.

00:20:57.202 --> 00:20:58.402
Try it and see.

00:20:59.668 --> 00:21:00.668
I'm kidding.

00:21:01.690 --> 00:21:02.721
Get some rest.

00:21:03.208 --> 00:21:04.402
Try not to worry too much.

00:21:07.307 --> 00:21:08.710
How can I not worry?

00:21:09.769 --> 00:21:12.704
None of the cats, big or small,
wants to talk to me.

00:21:15.935 --> 00:21:17.135
About the cats,

00:21:19.495 --> 00:21:20.775
I asked Dr. Pom.

00:21:21.486 --> 00:21:24.428
He said we could try talking to them
with a soft voice,

00:21:24.913 --> 00:21:26.279
so they won't be too scared of us.

00:21:26.615 --> 00:21:27.803
What should I say to them?

00:21:28.811 --> 00:21:29.811
Anything.

00:21:30.200 --> 00:21:33.014
Let's pretend I'm a cat.

00:21:35.647 --> 00:21:36.647
How?

00:21:38.527 --> 00:21:39.967
Come eat, nom nom.

00:21:40.734 --> 00:21:42.668
Come here. Have some nom nom.

00:21:43.560 --> 00:21:45.489
Ugh. That feels weird.

00:21:45.953 --> 00:21:46.953
It gives me chills.

00:21:47.213 --> 00:21:48.213
That was cute though.

00:21:48.823 --> 00:21:51.214
Cute how? You try then.

00:21:56.617 --> 00:21:57.693
It's gonna be okay.

00:21:59.550 --> 00:22:00.550
It'll pass.

00:22:02.202 --> 00:22:03.211
Don't be scared.

00:22:03.439 --> 00:22:04.439
Don't worry too much.

00:22:09.770 --> 00:22:10.915
I'm here always.

00:22:12.430 --> 00:22:13.430
What?

00:22:18.099 --> 00:22:19.459
I'm here, always.

00:22:22.498 --> 00:22:23.498
Hey!

00:22:24.964 --> 00:22:26.124
Go. Get out of here.

00:22:28.341 --> 00:22:29.144
Goodnight.

00:22:29.292 --> 00:22:30.292
I can't hear you.

00:22:30.668 --> 00:22:31.668
Goodnight.

00:22:31.816 --> 00:22:32.823
Just go already.

00:22:41.777 --> 00:22:42.449
Sweet dreams.

00:22:42.501 --> 00:22:43.501
Go.

00:23:02.607 --> 00:23:07.076
The early cat…
gets the coffee.

00:23:12.115 --> 00:23:15.006
MUAH MUAH

00:23:16.421 --> 00:23:17.425
Getting back at me?

00:23:18.610 --> 00:23:19.623
Then give it back.

00:23:27.313 --> 00:23:28.313
So…

00:23:28.987 --> 00:23:30.318
have you talked to Leo yet?

00:23:32.703 --> 00:23:33.703
Not yet.

00:23:34.388 --> 00:23:36.237
I'll wait until things cool down
a little more.

00:23:41.983 --> 00:23:42.983
Leo.

00:23:43.632 --> 00:23:44.632
Where are you going?

00:23:48.293 --> 00:23:49.293
I'm moving out.

00:23:51.330 --> 00:23:52.200
Don't worry.

00:23:52.294 --> 00:23:55.017
Once I get a new job,
I'll send money for the café repairs.

00:23:55.428 --> 00:23:56.623
Where are you going to stay?

00:23:56.790 --> 00:23:57.790
Have you found a place?

00:23:58.136 --> 00:23:59.136
That's my problem.

00:23:59.247 --> 00:24:00.811
Where I'm going
is none of your concern.

00:24:03.490 --> 00:24:04.490
Leo!

00:24:18.298 --> 00:24:19.624
What happened?

00:24:20.519 --> 00:24:22.205
Why is the café such a mess?

00:24:22.560 --> 00:24:23.560
Huh?

00:24:25.722 --> 00:24:26.906
How did you get here?

00:24:27.761 --> 00:24:28.910
I asked your grandmother.

00:24:29.912 --> 00:24:30.916
Why are you here?

00:24:32.100 --> 00:24:33.107
To apologize?

00:24:33.702 --> 00:24:35.262
Or did you just remember
you're our dad?

00:24:39.429 --> 00:24:40.429
Leo.

00:24:41.221 --> 00:24:42.221
Lynx.

00:24:44.233 --> 00:24:45.233
I'm sorry…

00:24:46.598 --> 00:24:50.674
I was never there for you
as a father.

00:24:53.543 --> 00:24:55.403
Can you give me a chance
to make it up to you?

00:25:03.053 --> 00:25:05.302
Just tell me
how much money you need.

00:25:05.815 --> 00:25:09.077
For the café, for school,
or for anything,

00:25:09.102 --> 00:25:10.782
I'm happy to support you
however I can.

00:25:15.682 --> 00:25:16.762
I just ask for one thing.

00:25:23.172 --> 00:25:24.492
Unless it's absolutely necessary,

00:25:26.078 --> 00:25:28.230
don't ever show up
at my place like that again.

00:25:29.308 --> 00:25:31.304
I'm happy to support you
however I can.

00:25:31.502 --> 00:25:32.604
I just ask for one thing.

00:25:32.944 --> 00:25:34.313
Stay away from that house.

00:25:34.722 --> 00:25:36.166
I'll contact you when I can.

00:25:36.563 --> 00:25:37.563
So?

00:25:39.420 --> 00:25:40.612
Don't hold back.

00:25:41.333 --> 00:25:43.092
You can tell me anything you need.

00:25:43.414 --> 00:25:46.046
It's the only thing
I can compensate you two.

00:25:46.913 --> 00:25:48.597
- Go ahead. Tell me.
- Keep your money.

00:25:51.481 --> 00:25:52.884
I'll take care of my brother alone.

00:25:58.149 --> 00:25:59.149
Please leave.

00:26:01.713 --> 00:26:02.713
If possible,

00:26:04.778 --> 00:26:05.944
don't ever come to us again.

00:26:06.917 --> 00:26:08.000
Keep your money.

00:26:09.806 --> 00:26:13.001
We'll take care of our kids alone.

00:26:14.144 --> 00:26:15.516
Don't ever show your face again.

00:26:15.841 --> 00:26:17.328
I don't want the kids

00:26:17.822 --> 00:26:19.527
to know they have a father
as awful as you!

00:26:19.988 --> 00:26:20.996
I used to be sad

00:26:23.778 --> 00:26:25.501
that I didn't have a father
like other kids.

00:26:28.036 --> 00:26:29.093
Now I understand

00:26:30.970 --> 00:26:32.650
why Mom chose to tell me
you were dead.

00:27:05.407 --> 00:27:11.197
Leo. It's okay.

00:27:11.548 --> 00:27:12.548
It's okay.

00:27:12.919 --> 00:27:13.919
It's okay.

00:27:15.527 --> 00:27:16.527
It's okay.

00:27:17.660 --> 00:27:18.660
It's okay.

00:27:19.888 --> 00:27:20.888
It's okay.

00:27:21.502 --> 00:27:22.632
Think about your baby first.

00:27:22.674 --> 00:27:24.912
It's okay. Think about your baby first.

00:27:29.857 --> 00:27:32.348
♪ Used to ache with pain ♪

00:27:32.513 --> 00:27:38.218
♪ It feels so good now
with you by my side ♪

00:27:39.080 --> 00:27:43.688
♪ I'll hold you close, won't let go,
won't let it fade ♪

00:27:43.993 --> 00:27:48.875
♪ This warm and steady space you made ♪

00:27:48.941 --> 00:27:56.538
♪ 'Cause it's you, I found my home ♪

00:28:02.300 --> 00:28:03.100
Tiger.

00:28:03.246 --> 00:28:04.406
Help me bring the laundry in.

00:28:04.590 --> 00:28:05.596
It's about to rain.

00:28:19.181 --> 00:28:20.399
Did you feed the cats?

00:28:23.739 --> 00:28:24.739
Yes.

00:28:25.987 --> 00:28:27.347
But none of them have come to eat.

00:29:01.102 --> 00:29:02.102
Lynx.

00:29:04.745 --> 00:29:07.401
I'm sorry for the damage to the café.

00:29:10.056 --> 00:29:11.656
I didn't mean for any of this to happen.

00:29:12.577 --> 00:29:15.313
Mm. Forget it.

00:29:18.548 --> 00:29:19.548
It's okay.

00:29:20.442 --> 00:29:23.744
We just have to fix what's broken.

00:29:27.076 --> 00:29:28.210
Help me fix it, okay?

00:29:32.097 --> 00:29:33.097
Okay.

00:29:42.404 --> 00:29:43.906
And whoever was eavesdropping…

00:29:45.623 --> 00:29:46.710
has to help fix it too.

00:29:48.594 --> 00:29:49.594
Alright.

00:29:51.994 --> 00:29:53.013
I'm here to help you now.

00:30:32.080 --> 00:30:33.840
JOHN WICK

00:30:34.729 --> 00:30:35.729
I'm sorry.

00:30:35.950 --> 00:30:38.203
I was going to pay off the debt
as fast as I could.

00:30:39.058 --> 00:30:40.287
And then all this happened.

00:30:41.859 --> 00:30:43.474
Do I look like someone
who wants money?

00:30:46.898 --> 00:30:47.931
You are the creditor.

00:30:48.603 --> 00:30:50.088
If not money,
then what do you want?

00:30:51.702 --> 00:30:52.702
You…

00:30:59.703 --> 00:31:01.433
You'll let me have this as interest, right?

00:31:03.338 --> 00:31:04.514
Why would you want that?

00:31:05.030 --> 00:31:06.710
Mom left that picture up for way too long.

00:31:06.764 --> 00:31:09.330
Look, it doesn't look good.

00:31:10.440 --> 00:31:12.510
There are these things called
photo editing apps, you know.

00:31:12.534 --> 00:31:13.580
Learn to use one.

00:31:15.434 --> 00:31:17.798
You used to look at my picture
all the time, didn't you?

00:31:22.089 --> 00:31:23.495
Krapor told me everything.

00:31:24.783 --> 00:31:28.807
Every time you came here,
you would secretly blink at my picture.

00:31:30.378 --> 00:31:31.417
I was here to see Jiro.

00:31:31.723 --> 00:31:32.723
You sure?

00:31:34.269 --> 00:31:35.269
Like this?

00:31:47.284 --> 00:31:48.284
Right?

00:32:04.209 --> 00:32:05.219
Hey you guys…

00:32:05.896 --> 00:32:07.892
Lynx and Leo are waiting
for you at the café.

00:32:09.647 --> 00:32:11.106
They have something to show you too.

00:32:12.999 --> 00:32:15.328
You once gave this dad
and Papa a chance.

00:32:17.068 --> 00:32:18.706
Can you give Leo a chance too?

00:32:21.091 --> 00:32:22.417
He's waiting for you over there.

00:32:39.418 --> 00:32:40.622
I'm just like you all.

00:32:41.160 --> 00:32:43.560
I came here because I was abandoned.

00:32:44.309 --> 00:32:47.196
But that day, I was the one
left you behind.

00:32:48.450 --> 00:32:50.003
You must've been really scared, right?

00:32:50.825 --> 00:32:51.825
I'm sorry.

00:32:52.112 --> 00:32:53.197
From now on, I promise you

00:32:54.737 --> 00:32:56.507
I won't leave you again.

00:33:30.281 --> 00:33:31.310
Thank you, Granny Juu.

00:33:40.688 --> 00:33:42.324
To celebrate our restored café,

00:33:43.140 --> 00:33:46.909
this servant will cook a special meal
for all our cat bosses.

00:33:50.452 --> 00:33:52.852
I didn't forget you two cats either.

00:33:53.682 --> 00:33:55.123
With extra crispy fried eggs.

00:33:57.915 --> 00:33:58.925
Thank you, bro.

00:34:01.166 --> 00:34:02.166
Is it good?

00:34:07.329 --> 00:34:09.912
Wow. It's as good as Mom's cooking.

00:34:11.788 --> 00:34:12.798
So when are you moving?

00:34:19.568 --> 00:34:20.800
Didn't you already pack?

00:34:22.775 --> 00:34:23.787
How about tonight?

00:34:26.948 --> 00:34:30.808
Well, I've been thinking...

00:34:31.154 --> 00:34:33.203
I mean moving out
of my room into Mom's.

00:34:34.474 --> 00:34:35.713
I want my room back.

00:34:41.280 --> 00:34:42.284
Thank you, bro.

00:34:45.817 --> 00:34:46.817
No big deal.

00:34:47.636 --> 00:34:49.120
It's my duty as a brother, after all.

00:34:50.053 --> 00:34:51.590
Hey, what are you doing?

00:34:54.403 --> 00:34:57.052
You can let me have
this fried egg too, right?

00:34:57.319 --> 00:34:59.103
No, that's too much. Give it back.

00:34:59.310 --> 00:35:00.121
Can't you let me have it?

00:35:00.146 --> 00:35:01.186
Give it back.

00:35:01.435 --> 00:35:02.188
Can't you give it to your brother?

00:35:02.231 --> 00:35:03.231
Not this.

00:35:03.691 --> 00:35:05.685
Come on. You're breaking it.

00:35:06.022 --> 00:35:07.235
No, you can't have it.

00:35:07.269 --> 00:35:08.291
Just give it to him.

00:35:09.181 --> 00:35:10.415
I'll make you another one.

00:35:13.481 --> 00:35:14.481
Fine.

00:35:17.668 --> 00:35:19.216
Has the party started? We're here.

00:35:20.384 --> 00:35:21.276
When there's food involved,

00:35:21.387 --> 00:35:22.787
I'm here in a flash.

00:35:41.810 --> 00:35:44.837
Excuse me. I must be going.

00:35:45.742 --> 00:35:46.742
Krapor.

00:35:51.160 --> 00:35:52.628
Krapor, that's the café's chair.

00:35:56.288 --> 00:35:57.088
Sorry.

00:35:57.259 --> 00:35:58.269
Get home safe.

00:36:01.877 --> 00:36:03.061
Will he make it home alright?

00:36:06.472 --> 00:36:07.492
What about you, Dr. Pom?

00:36:08.120 --> 00:36:09.128
You sure you're good?

00:36:10.204 --> 00:36:11.318
Need me to call you a ride?

00:36:12.280 --> 00:36:13.905
I'm fine. It's just around the corner.

00:36:14.117 --> 00:36:15.123
Just a short walk.

00:36:17.490 --> 00:36:18.490
I'm sorry…

00:36:19.404 --> 00:36:22.524
for saying I didn't like you before.

00:36:25.619 --> 00:36:26.619
Actually…

00:36:28.120 --> 00:36:29.416
you're a good person.

00:36:30.643 --> 00:36:31.763
A good advisor

00:36:32.734 --> 00:36:33.918
for both people and cats.

00:36:36.019 --> 00:36:37.019
Me too.

00:36:38.142 --> 00:36:39.142
I'm sorry…

00:36:39.449 --> 00:36:41.607
for saying you didn't seem
like an animal lover.

00:36:42.412 --> 00:36:43.412
Actually…

00:36:44.829 --> 00:36:46.155
you really take good care of the cats

00:36:46.179 --> 00:36:47.413
especially the café owner cat.

00:36:49.103 --> 00:36:50.103
That one,

00:36:50.561 --> 00:36:52.215
Je Meow once said
he was the toughest one.

00:36:53.009 --> 00:36:54.529
I thought she was kidding at the time.

00:36:56.413 --> 00:36:59.181
There's one more thing
I'm still worried about.

00:37:00.450 --> 00:37:04.018
If it's about the cats here,
you don't need to worry.

00:37:04.863 --> 00:37:06.413
They've already forgiven us.

00:37:07.002 --> 00:37:08.722
They're back to enjoying
eating like before.

00:37:11.790 --> 00:37:15.904
There's another cat who hasn't forgiven
himself yet about his mom.

00:37:17.173 --> 00:37:18.500
He's still blaming himself.

00:37:19.144 --> 00:37:22.598
Please take extra care of that one.

00:37:24.787 --> 00:37:25.953
I'll leave him in your hands.

00:37:42.006 --> 00:37:43.646
Don't stare at the cat pictures too long.

00:37:44.105 --> 00:37:45.401
You'll fall for them like I did.

00:37:46.391 --> 00:37:47.854
I'm not staring at the cat pictures.

00:37:48.053 --> 00:37:50.934
JE MEOW

00:37:51.190 --> 00:37:52.332
My mom was really amazing.

00:37:53.799 --> 00:37:54.839
She raised me

00:37:56.561 --> 00:37:58.622
and all these kids.

00:38:03.298 --> 00:38:04.978
Every single one of them
is such a handful.

00:38:06.394 --> 00:38:07.594
I can't imagine

00:38:08.568 --> 00:38:09.617
if it were me,

00:38:10.303 --> 00:38:11.575
how I would've managed.

00:38:16.699 --> 00:38:17.699
But today…

00:38:19.775 --> 00:38:21.385
you did exactly what she would've done.

00:38:27.322 --> 00:38:28.516
You did really great already.

00:38:37.014 --> 00:38:38.222
Being a big brother

00:38:39.712 --> 00:38:40.892
is hard, isn't it?

00:38:44.738 --> 00:38:45.806
Don't carry it alone.

00:38:47.091 --> 00:38:48.188
You can leave it to me.

00:38:49.364 --> 00:38:50.364
Right here.

00:38:59.000 --> 00:39:00.994
JE MEOW

00:39:25.914 --> 00:39:27.020
You did really great.

00:39:31.828 --> 00:39:33.508
Hey! Who made my bro cry?

00:39:36.724 --> 00:39:37.730
You crying, Lynx?

00:39:37.768 --> 00:39:38.800
Tiger made you cry?

00:39:40.128 --> 00:39:41.128
I didn't.

00:39:43.040 --> 00:39:44.040
Kidding.

00:39:44.128 --> 00:39:45.172
Why are you sad?

00:39:46.596 --> 00:39:47.655
Let's drink more.

00:39:48.242 --> 00:39:49.243
Don't be sad.

00:39:49.370 --> 00:39:50.385
Fine, I'm not sad.

00:39:51.527 --> 00:39:52.527
Come on.

00:39:57.581 --> 00:39:59.117
You drank way more than
you can handle.

00:39:59.412 --> 00:40:01.015
Next time, I'll just carry you home.

00:40:04.051 --> 00:40:07.294
Why go home? Sleep here.

00:40:09.122 --> 00:40:10.504
Is this the real you?

00:40:12.306 --> 00:40:13.306
Why?

00:40:13.593 --> 00:40:15.988
Didn't you just say
you'd carry me home?

00:40:17.537 --> 00:40:19.097
If this is what you're like when drunk,

00:40:19.150 --> 00:40:20.295
I'm not talking to you.

00:40:21.883 --> 00:40:22.883
Hey.

00:40:24.340 --> 00:40:25.398
I'm already sober.

00:40:26.237 --> 00:40:28.530
That little amount
can't do anything to me.

00:40:41.149 --> 00:40:42.149
Lynx.

00:40:43.465 --> 00:40:44.487
Don't do that again.

00:40:49.738 --> 00:40:50.738
Why?

00:40:51.123 --> 00:40:53.122
You stole a cheek kiss
from me the other day.

00:40:54.404 --> 00:40:55.908
That was just a cheek kiss.

00:40:56.983 --> 00:40:58.105
Okay, fine.

00:40:59.813 --> 00:41:01.006
You don't need to sleep here.

00:41:02.625 --> 00:41:06.032
Just a goodnight kiss then.

00:41:18.126 --> 00:41:19.204
You don't love me anymore?

00:41:31.654 --> 00:41:32.774
Satisfied now?

00:41:33.190 --> 00:41:34.190
Yes.

00:41:41.904 --> 00:41:42.918
What about you?

00:41:44.383 --> 00:41:45.452
Are you already satisfied?

00:41:55.267 --> 00:41:56.267
No, Lynx.

00:41:57.163 --> 00:41:58.163
Don't do this.

00:42:28.057 --> 00:42:29.123
I warned you.

00:42:30.997 --> 00:42:32.073
Don't do this.

00:43:30.132 --> 00:43:33.138
(Next Episode) Isn't that Lynx, the
café owner who's officially off the market?

00:43:33.162 --> 00:43:34.411
I don't like being teased.

00:43:35.167 --> 00:43:37.822
I get awkward and I
don't know how to react.

00:43:38.302 --> 00:43:40.216
We don't look like a couple, do we?

00:43:41.079 --> 00:43:42.079
Lynx.

00:43:42.637 --> 00:43:44.024
Don't worry about other people.

00:43:44.301 --> 00:43:45.320
Just be yourself.

00:43:45.712 --> 00:43:48.032
If I have to wear this kind of suit,
no matter where it is,

00:43:48.245 --> 00:43:49.885
I'd want the person next to me to be you.